nl.helixsoft.graph

Class GmlFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.helixsoft.graph.GmlFormat

  • public final class GmlFormat
extends java.lang.Object
    Note that the node attribute "label" will be used as the node identifier during GML import in Cytoscape. The Node id itself will be converted to an integer. The formatter will warn if you try to supply label as an attribute.
